cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.DS, cs.SE, cs.DB

The paper discusses a novel approach to analyse large amounts of intercepted network traffic based on network metadata. This involves the use of techniques from computer security (cs.CR), networking (cs.NI), data structures (cs.DS), software engineering (cs.SE), and databases (cs.DB). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
